### 구간 추가 API

### 가산에서 하행 방향으로 구로 추가

POST http://localhost:8080/sections
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "lineName" : "7호선",
  "direction" : "Down",
  "standardStationName" : "가산",
  "additionalStationName" : "구로",
  "distance" : 10
}

### Response

HTTP/1.1 201
Location: /lines/1
Content-Type: application/json
Transfer-Encoding: chunked
Date: Fri, 19 May 2023 05:49:36 GMT
Keep-Alive: timeout=60
Connection: keep-alive

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "7호선",
  "color": "bg-olive-600",
  "sections": [
    {
      "id": 8,
      "distance": 10,
      "previousStation": {
        "id": 5,
        "name": "구로"
      },
      "nextStation": {
        "id": 1,
        "name": "가산"
      }
    }
  ]
}

