### 구간 삭제 API

### 7호선에서 대림 역을 삭제 (사이 역)

DELETE http://localhost:8080/sections?lineid=1&stationid=3

### Response

HTTP/1.1 204
Date: Fri, 19 May 2023 06:03:12 GMT
Keep-Alive: timeout=60
Connection: keep-alive

### 7호선에서 가산 역을 삭제 (종점)

DELETE http://localhost:8080/sections?lineid=1&stationid=1

